credit_line: Museum purchase through gift of Mrs. John Innes Kane
title: Dog
provenance: From the collection of Baron Alphonse de Rothschild, Vienna, formerly in the collection of Baron Nathaniel de Rothschild, Vienna, who is said to have received it from his father, Ansel de Rothschild.
description: Figure of a brown-spotted pug with cropped ears and a long trail.  Blue collar banded and inscribed in gold "ANO 1741."  Collar secured by padlock.
name: Figure
